{"comments":"Attested Scheduling — Cryptographically verified scheduling primitives.\n\nThis module composes the Attestation pillar with the Scheduling schema\nto provide verifiable, tamper-evident scheduling actions:\n\n- **AttestedEvent**: An event with cryptographic proof of creation time\n- **AttestedInvite**: An invitation with verifiable sender identity\n- **AttestedRSVP**: A response with proof of responder and timestamp\n\n## Why Attested Scheduling?\n\nAt billion-agent scale, scheduling requires:\n1. **Non-repudiation**: Proof that an action occurred\n2. **Tamper detection**: Verify content hasn't been modified\n3. **Deterministic identity**: Same content = same hash\n4. **x402 compatibility**: Foundation for on-chain verification\n\n## Usage\n\n```purescript\n-- Create an attested event\nattestedEvent <- attestEvent myEvent currentTimestamp\n\n-- Verify the event hasn't been tampered with\nisValid = verifyEvent attestedEvent\n\n-- Get the attestation proof\nproof = getEventAttestation attestedEvent\n```\n","declarations":[{"children":[],"comments":"An event with cryptographic attestation.\n\nThe attestation proves:\n- When the event was created/attested\n- The exact content of the event at that time\n- A deterministic ID derived from content\n","info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"typeSynonym","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Attestation","Attested"],"Attested"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Scheduling","Event"],"Event"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[131,45],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Scheduling/Attested.purs","start":[131,1]},"title":"AttestedEvent"},{"children":[],"comments":"An invitation with cryptographic attestation.\n\nThe attestation proves:\n- When the invite was sent\n- Who sent the invite (via content hash)\n- The exact invitation details\n","info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"typeSynonym","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Attestation","Attested"],"Attested"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Scheduling","Invite"],"Invite"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[139,47],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Scheduling/Attested.purs","start":[139,1]},"title":"AttestedInvite"},{"children":[],"comments":"An RSVP response with cryptographic attestation.\n\nThe attestation proves:\n- When the response was made\n- Who responded (via contact info in content)\n- The exact response (Accepted, Declined, etc.)\n","info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"typeSynonym","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Attestation","Attested"],"Attested"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Scheduling","Attested"],"RSVPResponse"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[147,51],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Scheduling/Attested.purs","start":[147,1]},"title":"AttestedRSVP"},{"children":[],"comments":"RSVP response with context (who responded to what)\n","info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"typeSynonym","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Record"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["inviteId",{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"String"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["contactId",{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"String"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["response",{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Scheduling","RSVP"],"RSVP"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["comment",{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Maybe"],"Maybe"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"String"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"anno